[resource]
script = ExtResource("3_o7dfl")
category = 3
text = "The Tyrant of Warfare, Renata Oflugr is the current Chief Director of Execution and Operations (CDEO) for the Blue Caps. Renata is a 54 year old woman from a family of immigrants from Eastern Befre. Being the CDEO is quite an influential position and Renata is a very adamant and stern person, which has lead many higher-ups to be quite unhappy with her decision making. She typically disagrees with a lot that the parliment says and that feeds to their fear of her. Yet people in the army love her, and she has one of the highest popularity of any of the recent CDEO's of the army.

Renata was a child that grew up in a relatively poor household in a town in Eastern Befre called Polsgaard. Polsgaard has a large immigrant population and Renata was one of them. She was a kid with little social skills but that was mostly due to her own decision to isolate. The only person who was quite like Renata was her teacher and personal school tutor Mr Hyesgar. Mr Hyesgar was quite similar to her in personality, he also was her only friend at school. He was a veteran in the army, quite a high position one too, and all the stories he told reached Renata. His influence led her to want to join the army. Mr Hyesgar is also from the nearby continent Volin, which is one of the factors that makes Renata so friendly to people of Volin.

Upon joining the army, Renata slid right through multiple ranks, due to being a perfect fit for what army officials needed to be. She first became a commander, then Polsgaard official, then her Zone Official then finally at 39 became a County General of her home county. After 11 years of being in that role, after an impressive campaign, overwelming vote popularity from friendly officers in her adjacent roles and even favourable opinions from the retiring CDEO, Renata became the first ever second generation immigrant to be at the highest position in the army. Every year the Blue Caps do a vote on if the CDEO is doing a good job, and Renata consistently breaks records for popularity polls as her results over the 4 years have all been higher than any previously recorded records.

During her time as CDEO nothing too incredible has happened, but she does remain a leader who is very risk-free. Many politicians see her as reckless and trecherous for her belief in an open Befre and some for being an immigrants child. Renata has heavy contacts and friends who live in Volin, which contributes to her open opinions to allow researchers into her country. There are rumours of her training up researchers \"into the army\" so she can do the Icy Hollows research herself, but that would lead to possibly large turmoil between the two disagreeing parties. When she was 32, during Lafefs Coup over at Zengef, when the tensions were brewing, Renata offered to bring her loyal army over to help out her friend in the war. The friend, Lank Follas, refused knowing it would lose Renata her job which is her passion. Multiple times she was willing to risk her career for friends abroad, but she is yet to done so, but now as she is the CDEO of the Blue Caps, she can do as she pleases. No longer risking her job, just ruining her already strained relationship with the Befre Parliment."
id = 29
name = "Renata Oflugr"
